                </li>
            </ul>

                <!-- Introduction -->
                <div class="row">

                    <p>Give For Free raises funds for your favorite charity - with a TWIST.</p><br>
                    <p>Instead of donating money, post your preloved items on our platform.</p><br>
                    <p>Anyone who 'buys' your items pays the money directly to your chosen charity.</p><br>
                    <p>You can shop for items here too. Simply donate to a charity to 'buy' the item.</p><br>
                    <p><b>Charities benefit. You benefit. The Environment benefits.</b></p>

                </div>
