                    <h6>Rules</h6>
                </li>
            </ul>

            <!-- Introduction -->
            <div class="row">

                <ol style="text-align:left">
                    <li>
                        For any grievances, please inform admin at giveforfreefeedback@gmail.com. Please do not post your grievances on the platform. This is to prevent members from debating and breaking the joy of giving.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        All prices shown will be paid directly to the charity. Postage and handling fees, if any, should be specified separately in the item description.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        No monetary exchange is allowed between members on Give For Free. If there is suspicion on price or request for cash on delivery, please inform admin.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        No begging / pestering / touting / spamming members. Report any such activities to admin immediately.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        Please donate promptly once a gift has been given to you. If the donation is not made within 24 hours, giver can inform admin to give the gift to someone else instead.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        Similarly, please deliver gift promptly after donation has been made. 
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        Admin reserves the right to remove any items on the platform or ban members who do not follow these rules.
                    </li>
                </ol>
            </div>
